Interface Summary
MetricalEntry Defines the requirements for an entry in a node of a Metrical Index.
MetricalNode<N extends MetricalNode<N,E>,E extends MetricalEntry> Defines the requirements for an object that can be used as a node in a Metrical Index.
 

Class Summary
MetricalIndex<O extends DatabaseObject,D extends Distance<D>,N extends MetricalNode<N,E>,E extends MetricalEntry> Abstract super class for all metrical index classes.
